reviewText: I enjoy watching Ji Chang Wook's and his martial arts move.  He is good looking. I like happy ending
Love this drama! Worth buying. It was well packaged and came before delivery date. Subtitle are good throughout the drama.

This version is a compressed version. Picture quality could be much better. A few parts freezes. Will wait for a better version.  Also, being a collector, this version was plainly packed in plastic sleeves. I prefer the digipak, booklet versions. Plus, strange that there is no distributor or manufacturer information shown while watching this compared to other Korean dramas that I have seen.

This series makes me so happy!!! I am so excited that my sister got it for me for my birthday. Ji Chang Wook is amazing, the plot is flawless and I love it so much. Definitely makes you feel all the feels :)
Probably my favorite K drama ever. I usually just watch on Drama Fever, but this one is worth owning.
One of my favorites. Loved it.
